Package: asp21bpspline
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian P Splines for Location Scale Regression
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-07-24
Author: Valentin, Jonathan, Jan
Maintainer: Who to complain to <jonathan.henrich@stud.uni-goettingen.de>
Description: The asp21bpspline package allows to fit a basis spline model for the location and scale of a univariate response variable. It contains both a likelihood based method that allows for explicit regularization and a bayesian method that implicitly produces regularized splines.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.7),
         RcppEigen,
         generics (>= 0.1.0),
         mvtnorm,
         lmls, 
         ggplot2
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
